.card.card--full-width.styleguide-intro
  .clearfix
    %h1.split--left.copy--title UI Colours
    .split--right.filter--links
      %a{ href: "javascript:sortBy(lightToDark)" } Light to dark
      |
      %a{ href: "javascript:sortBy(darkToLight)" } Dark to light
  %p.copy--body
    These are the colours outside of the primary palettes that are used within the sass. They are defined in 
    %a{href: 'https://github.com/lonelyplanet/rizzo/blob/master/app/assets/stylesheets/_variables/_colour_theme.sass'}
      colour_theme.sass

- get_colours('_colour_theme').each do |group|
  = render 'styleguide/partials/colour', group: group

= render 'styleguide/javascripts/luminosity'